channel.title: [508]Gods army server v2! dual HD and LD, skills and barrow armor effect!
channel.description:
[size=10pt][u][b]news: you need to delete "fletching.java" i forgot to delete it.[/b][/u][/size]
Hi and i am now ready to release Gods army server v2
features: source - xeloxoft release smallscreen
[b]features(version 0):[/b] - 70% GodWars (Not sure, maybe 60-70%) - My own minigame, The Great 5! - Kalphite morphing! - Every npc ingame have the right emotes, except the ones i haven't found! - Commands, teleports and so on. - every modern spell is working, summoning base added! - NPC aggresion, following isn't added! - Npc attack 60% - Player Combat 70% - Special attack for all the godswords, effects on all except Bandos! - All the godwars object working! - ::item command for everyone, item restricted! - Item on Item - Global Objects - Fullscreen client, server! - Not to easy, not to hard to TRAIN or MAKING CASH! - Alot of special attacks! - Lunar, Modern and Ancient Magicks! - Single pk! - Working Npc update masks! - Bounty hunter - Flames on KBD (A bit bugged) - Fireshield needed (KBD) - CW Base - Jad have all the atks, mage, range and melee. - poisoning! And ALOT more
[b]features(version 1):[/b] potions thieving better eating method prayer membership base herblore teletabs base for crafting +all from version 0
[b]features(version 2):[/b] able to test staking and trade fletching crafting godsword making Updated bh HD Dual HD and LD shops custom barrow effects
